dataIdInfo.envirDesc: Microsoft Windows 7 Version 6.1 (Build 7601) Service Pack 1; Esri ArcGIS 10.2.0.3348
dataIdInfo.idCredit: This spatial dataset was processed by the Information and Communication Technology Management Service (ICTMS) of the Department of Social Welfare and Development (DSWD) - Republic of the Philippines, from various sources: Philippine GIS Data Clearinghouse (PhilGIS) for Luzon and Visayas, Office of the Presidential Adviser on the Peace Process (OPAPP) for Mindanao, Digital Atlas for Kalayaan Group of Islands, and AAG Land Surveying for Bajo de Masinloc (Panatag Shoal). The entries of the attribute table came from the National Statistics Coordination Board (NSCB).
dataIdInfo.idPurp: This spatial dataset is intended for all non-commercial mapping initiatives of the Department of Social Welfare and Development (DSWD), Republic of the Philippines. This does not bear any legal basis on administrative boundaries.
dataIdInfo.idAbs:
This spatial dataset shows all of the Philippines' 1,634 cities and municipalities. The following is a description of its attribute table:

  • REG_PSGC = Philippine Standard Geographic Code of the Region

  • REG_NAME = Name of the Region

  • PROV_PSGC = Philippine Standard Geographic Code of the Province

  • PROV_NAME = Name of the Province

  • MC_PSGC = Philippine Standard Geographic Code of the Municipality/City

  • MC_NAME = Name of the Municipality/City

  • BRGYS = Number of Barangays in the Municipality/City
